not touching, then freeze for approx. <b>1 hour<b>. Place partially frozen meat <b>(250 g<b> at a time) in mixing bowl then mince <strong>8-15 sec\/\/speed 6-7<\/strong>, depending on the type of meat and the desired consistency. Tip out and repeat process if necessary with another <b>250 g<b> partially frozen meat.<br><br>IMPORTANT: do not put fully frozen meat, nor partially frozen meat in one large piece in mixing bowl because there is a risk of damage to the blades. The meat must be thawed slightly and in pieces."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","30m","15 pieces"]}